overview:
Agicent Technologies is a globally serving software consulting, development, and R&D services provider, specialized in the areas of next generation Mobile Apps, Web, Enterprise, and Embedded/ Telecom.

Agicent is a small but growing team of 25+ technologists primarily serving customers that include (but not limited to):

  • Software product start-ups (early stage ISVs).
  • Growing/ Established Software Product Companies (ISVs)
  • Enterprises (of any size, cutting across various verticals)

Agicent’s more than 75 % of customer base is from USA, followed by Europe and then Middle East.

Following are some of Agicent’s prime Technology Excellence areas: Mobile - iOS (iPhone Apps/ iPad Apps), Android, Windows, BB, HTML5, Mobile Web App/ Hybrid App Web - Open Source/ LAMP, eCommerce, .NET driven web solutions, Java web development, legacy ASP.NET, Server programming, Web services Enterprise - .NET, Sharepoint, BI, Web/ PHP based Enterprise solutions. Embedded/ Telecom - C/ C++, Embedded C, RTOS, Assembly, Firmware development, SCADA/ Telemetry

Agicent is headquartered in Noida, India with a sales & delivery office in NJ, USA.
